OL,4,Cwoman given suspended sentence
OL,6,FA burglar was confronted by a 100-year-
OL,7,Fold woman when he crept into her
OL,8,Fbedroom to find items to sell money
OL,9,Ffor drugs.
OL,11,FRichard Allanson, 38, has earlier
OL,12,Ftried to steal from a 65-year-old
OL,13,Fresident at the Waltham Court
OL,14,Fretirement complex in Beverley in July
OL,15,Flast year.
OL,17,FThe pensioner warned Allanson to get
OL,18,Fout when he heard him trying the door
OL,19,Fat 7:30pm, before heading to 100-year-
OL,20,Fold woman's bedroom where he stifled
OL,21,Fthrough her jewellery box.
