OL,6,FAllanson later fled to the communal
OL,7,Farea of the retirement block.JWhen
OL,8,Fpolice arrived, he was found slumped
OL,9,Fover the wheel of a car.
OL,11,FDuring interview with officers, he
OL,12,Fsaid that he could not remember
OL,13,Fanything because of the drugs that he
OL,14,Fhad consumed.
OL,16,FThe woman later said that she had
OL,17,Fsince left the retirement
OL,18,Faccommodation because of her fears
OL,19,Fbecause she felt scared and was
OL,20,Fworried in case the burglar had a
OL,21,Fweapon and could have used it on her.
