OL,6,FMr Stuart said that Allanson targeted
OL,7,Fvulnerable victims but he was impaired
OL,8,Fdue to the amount of drugs that he had
OL,9,Ftaken, which made his actions
OL,10,Fimpulsive.
OL,12,FOliver Shipley, mitigating, said that
OL,13,Fhe claimed that he had been visiting
OL,14,Fan elderly friend at the retirement
OL,15,Fcomplex, and was "deeply sorry" for
OL,16,Fhis actions.
OL,18,FMr Shipley said that Allanson could
OL,19,Fnot explain why he was in the bedroom
OL,20,Fof a 100-year-old.
