OL,6,FJudge Gurdial Singh replied: "I can.
OL,7,FHe was committing burglary to steal
OL,8,Fjewellery to sell for drugs."
OL,10,FAllanson, of Mintfields Road, admitted
OL,11,Foffences of burglary and attempted
OL,12,Fburglary.
OL,14,FHe was given a 21-month suspended
OL,15,Fprison sentence, 120 hours' unpaid
OL,16,Fwork, a six-month alcohol treatment
OL,17,Fprogramme and 10 days' rehabilitation.
